title: T-shirt bag making machine US-XJBXJ-400*2
title_uz: Maykali paket ishlab chiqarish uskunasi US-XJBXJ-400*2
short_description: T-shirt bag production equipment also has different models. The equipment of this model has 2 sections and each section has the capacity to produce 60 to 150 products per minute and can produce up to 300 packages per minute in total. The size of this equipment, which weighs 1500 kg, is 6000*1450*1600 mm.
short_description_uz: Maykali paket ishlab chiqarish uskunalari ham turlicha modellarga ega. Bu modeldagi uskuna 2 bo'lmali va har bir bo'lma daqiqasiga 60 tadan 150 tagacha mahsulot ishlab chiqarish imkoniyatiga ega va daqiqasiga jami 300 tagacha paket ishlab chiqara oladi. Vazni 1500 kg ni tashkil etuvchi ushbu uskuna o'lchami 6000*1450*1600 mm dan iborat.

Размер данного оборудования весом 1500 кг составляет 6000*1450*1600 мм.
